  "text": "In other words, the geometric multiplicity of zero eigenvalue is L − N + 1. Clearly, the geometric multiplicity and the algebraic multiplicity of zero eigenvalue are equal, which implies that the corresponding Jordan block for each zero eigenvalue is size one from [CITATION_1] . That is, zero is a simple root of the minimal polynomial of L e .",
